KATSINA – Hon. Danlami Kurfi, a former member of the house of representatives from Katsina state, has advised APC senators, Reps members not to be carried away with the antics of the national chairman of the party, Senator Abdullahi Adamu as he does not keep to promises. Kurfi who gave the advice in an interview with newsmen in Katsina at the weekend, alleged that, the APC is a serial promise breaker. He urged those that lost the recently conducted primary elections of the party to defect to the PDP. “PDP is the only party where promises were kept. APC is a party of serial betrayers and promise breakers” . Kurfi recalled that when they lost the 2019 general elections, the party made promised them appointment, but were never honoured. “Even here in Katsina after loosing the election the state Governor, Alhaji Aminu Bello Masari made promises of appointment for them, but he didn’t honour” “The APC senators, reps members should not be carried away by the party chairman’s visit to the national assembly, Kurfi added, saying that, the PDP is the best party for them.